PN,41701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has said
OL,7,Fthe 24-hour strike by consultants and
OL,8,Fspecialist doctors on Thursday was
OL,9,F"highly regrettable" after almost
OL,10,F2,000 appointments were cancelled.
OL,12,FSpeaking at Stormont after a BMA
OL,13,Fdelegation representing the doctors
OL,14,Fmet with members of the Stormont
OL,15,FHealth Committee, the former UUP
OL,16,Fleader said he couldn't go above the
OL,17,F3.5% pay offer without first getting
OL,18,Fan endorsement from his Executive
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FBut Dr David Farren of the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Consultants Committee said
OL,8,F3.5% was below inflation and
OL,9,F"effectively a pay cut".
OL,11,FMinister Nesbitt said: "Doctor Farren
OL,12,Fknows, if he wanted me to go further
OL,13,Fthan that, I would have to go and seek
OL,14,Fagreement from my Executive
OL,15,Fcolleagues. To break that parity
OL,16,Farrangement would be repercussive for
OL,17,Fteachers, for police officers, prison
OL,18,Fofficers - in fact the entire public
OL,19,Fsector - and he knows that. I don't
OL,20,Fknow why he's saying what he's saying.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,F"I would just say gently to Dr Farren,
OL,7,Fhe thinks he's not half as well paid
OL,8,Fas his counterparts in England. A top
OL,9,Fof the range salary for a consultant
OL,10,Fhere with the 3.5% is #150,560, which
OL,11,Fis #41 more than he would get in
OL,12,FEngland. I know he's rightly worried
OL,13,Fabout dealing with this cost of living
OL,14,Fchallenge.
OL,16,F"Again, I would suggest 3.5% on
OL,17,F#150,000 makes life a bit easier than
OL,18,F3.3% on less than #40,000 - which is
OL,19,Fthe situation a Band 5 nurse finds
OL,20,Fthemselves in.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,F"I'm always concerned about the
OL,7,Fworkforce and doing what's right by
OL,8,Fthem, because I want them waking up in
OL,9,Fthe morning feeling good about life
OL,10,Fand looking forward to going on shift.
OL,11,FBut my primary concern is patient
OL,12,Fsafety.
OL,14,F"People are waiting far too long on
OL,15,Fwaiting lists. The people who are on
OL,16,Fstrike today did marvellous work last
OL,17,Ffinancial year in tackling the really
OL,18,Flong waits. Today, we're going to lose
OL,19,Fmomentum and I think that's highly
OL,20,Fregrettable."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FRoutine and elective procedures were
OL,7,Fcancelled across Northern Ireland from
OL,8,F7am. Emergency departments, intensive
OL,9,Fcare, and urgent care were to function
OL,10,Fnormally - with "Christmas Day-level"
OL,11,Fstaffing - in the walkout over "18
OL,12,Fyears of pay erosion".
OL,14,FAfter meeting with the Health
OL,15,FCommittee to discuss the pay dispute,
OL,16,FDr Farren warned of an escalation of
OL,17,Fthe strike action. Resident doctors
OL,18,Fare also to take part in a 24-hour
OL,19,Findustrial action on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FHe said: "I really hope not. It is a
OL,7,Flot for a doctor to take strike
OL,8,Faction. We go through our entire
OL,9,Fcareer looking after patients. For a
OL,10,Fdoctor to down tools and walk away
OL,11,Ffrom that really takes an awful lot.
OL,13,F"I would hope that today's action will
OL,14,Fbe enough to bring the minister and
OL,15,Fbring his officials to the table to
OL,16,Fhave a meaningful negotiation, not
OL,17,Fjust to say, 'I don't have any money'
OL,18,Fand 'could you ask the Executive for
OL,19,Fmore money for me, please?'. I think
OL,20,Fit has to be a meaningful negotiation
OL,21,Fand that will avert any further action.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,F"We are not looking to have strikes
OL,7,Ffor the sake of having strikes. We are
OL,8,Flooking to try and move this forward.
OL,9,FHowever, if the Minister doesn't come
OL,10,Fforward, I think escalation of action
OL,11,Fis the next step."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FDUP Health Spokesperson Diane Dodds,
OL,7,Fwho sits on the Committee, called for
OL,8,Fthe dispute to be resolved. She added:
OL,9,F"In Northern Ireland we have a
OL,10,Fpopulation of about 1.8 million
OL,11,Fpeople, and over half a million people
OL,12,Fare waiting on a first-time consultant
OL,13,Fappointment. That is a huge percentage
OL,14,Fof our population that are waiting on
OL,15,Fappointments with consultants. The
OL,16,Foutcome of a consultant strike can
OL,17,Fonly be missed hospital appointments
OL,18,Fand longer waiting lists. I'd really
OL,19,Furge both uh the consultants and the
OL,20,Fminister to resolve this issue in the
OL,21,Finterest of patients."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FHealth Committee Chairperson Philip
OL,7,FMcGuigan said the BMA members were
OL,8,F"extremely frustrated and angry" with
OL,9,Fthe Minister.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FThe Sinn Fein MLA added: "While this
OL,7,Fis obviously a very difficult
OL,8,Fsituation and I have sympathy with
OL,9,Fboth sides of the argument, we have a
OL,10,Fhealth minister - it is ultimately his
OL,11,Fresponsibility to ensure, first of
OL,12,Fall, there are safe staffing levels
OL,13,Fand that staff feel worthwhile because
OL,14,Fwithout staff, we can't have a
OL,15,Ffunctioning health service. What is
OL,16,Fneeded is good faith on the part of
OL,17,Fthe minister. He needs to engage with
OL,18,Fthe unions, proper negotiations to try
OL,19,Fand resolve this issue urgently.
OL,26,@nD@Krr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,F"I am concerned first of all that
OL,7,Fthere there is strike action, and that
OL,8,Fthe unions feel it's necessary to take
OL,9,Fstrike action. I'm also concerned
OL,10,Fabout the impact this will have on
OL,11,Fpatients. There will be people who
OL,12,Fwill have had procedures and
OL,13,Fappointments cancelled today. That
OL,14,FThat's disappointing. Uh so, the
OL,15,Fminister, as I say, ultimately has
OL,16,Fresponsibility. He needs to ensure
OL,17,Fthat he takes that responsibility
OL,18,Fseriously and work with the unions to
OL,19,Ftry and resolve this issue as quickly
OL,20,Fas possible."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
