PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782505102
OL,3,CHealth Minister won't go above 3.5%
OL,4,Cdeal for striking doctors
OL,6,FMeanwhile, some of Northern Ireland's
OL,7,Flowest-paid healthcare workers
OL,8,Fprotested over pay and conditions at
OL,9,FCraigavon Area Hospital saying staff
OL,10,Fwere demoralised and struggling to
OL,11,Fmake ends meet.
